OL,3,CTrial dates set in cases of men facing
OL,4,Cracially aggravated civil unrest
OL,5,Ccharges
OL,7,FTrial dates have been set by a judge
OL,8,Fin the court proceedings of two men
OL,9,Fwho stand accused of posting offensive
OL,10,Fracially-motivated content online.
OL,12,FBoth Gerard Glaister, 56, and Derek
OL,13,FHeggie, appeared at Carlisle Crown
OL,14,FCourt on Tuesday, separately, having
OL,15,Fpreviously attended magistrates' court
OL,16,Fhearings last week.
OL,18,FThey spoke to confirm their names and
OL,19,Fdates of birth, and each face one
OL,20,Fcharge.
