OL,3,CTrial dates set in cases of men facing
OL,4,Cracially aggravated civil unrest
OL,5,Ccharges
OL,7,FGlaister, of Hartington Street,
OL,8,FWorkington, stands accused of
OL,9,Fdisplaying Islamophobic and homophobic
OL,10,Fcontent on his Facebook profile.
OL,12,FHeggie, of Welsh Road, Carlisle, is
OL,13,Falleged to have posted racially
OL,14,Faggravated comments on a YouTube
OL,15,Fpodcast between 3 and 7 August.
OL,17,FNo pleas were formally entered by
OL,18,Feither man during their respective
OL,19,Fcourt hearings today in front of Judge
OL,20,FNicholas Barker. Both men have so far
OL,21,Findicated not guilty pleas.
