OL,4,Cracially aggravated civil unrest
OL,5,Ccharges
OL,7,FThey are due to formally enter their
OL,8,Fpleas at separate crown court hearings
OL,9,Fon 13 September.
OL,11,FGlaister's case was listed for trial
OL,12,Fin front of a jury. This is due to
OL,13,Fstart on 11 December with a time
OL,14,Festimate of two to three days.
OL,16,FHe has been granted bail in the
OL,17,Fmeantime. One condition of his bail
OL,18,Fprohibits him from posting anything on
OL,19,Fthe internet or on social media.
